## Summary
This documentation explains how to use Amplitude's conversion drivers feature to identify behaviors that lead to user conversions or drop-offs in funnel analyses, providing metrics like correlation score, behavior frequency, user engagement percentage, and conversion time to help understand which actions influence key outcomes in the customer journey.

